OL,6,GOfcom's proposals to remove some of
OL,7,Gthe limits on advertising on ITV 1,
OL,8,GChannel 4 and Channel 5 seem to
OL,9,Gstrike a sensible compromise.
OL,11,FTheir preferred way forward removes
OL,12,Fadditional restrictions on the
OL,13,Foverall volume of adverts and the
OL,14,Fmaximum length of breaks.
OL,16,FBut the tighter rules on the number
OL,17,Fof breaks within programmes would
OL,18,Fstay.
OL,20,FSo what might this mean in practice?
OL,3,CWhat would a change of PSB ad rules
OL,4,Cmean in practice?
