OL,6,FIt is worth focusing on ITV 1 simply
OL,7,Fbecause its audience is so much
OL,8,Fbigger than the other two channels.
OL,10,FOfcom has noted, as we have discussed
OL,11,Fbefore, that the main impact will be
OL,12,Fon the 6pm and 10pm News hours.
OL,14,FThey would be able to include a full
OL,15,F12 minutes of ads.
OL,17,FDuring the daytime, the 7am, 8am,
OL,18,F10am, 1pm and 2pm hours could see a
OL,19,Fslight rise in advertising. Typically
OL,20,Fthey have 10 minutes 30 seconds worth
OL,21,Fjust now.
OL,3,CWhat would a change of PSB ad rules
OL,4,Cmean in practice?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
