OL,6,FBut this could all be achieved by
OL,7,Fmaking the existing breaks longer `
OL,8,Fnot by additional interruptions.
OL,10,FFor instance the 10am and 1pm hours
OL,11,Fhave three breaks of 3 minutes 30
OL,12,Fseconds. They could potentially be
OL,13,Fextended to 4 minutes.
OL,15,FThe option of running longer internal
OL,16,Fbreaks could have pros and cons for
OL,17,Fviewers.
OL,19,FLonger internal breaks could mean
OL,20,Fbreaks between programmes could be
OL,21,Feliminated.
OL,3,CWhat would a change of PSB ad rules
OL,4,Cmean in practice?
