OL,6,FOfcom is also prepared to look at
OL,7,Fwhether to make no changes at all or
OL,8,Fallow a relaxation of the rule on the
OL,9,Fnumber of internal breaks.
OL,11,FThat could lead to two breaks during
OL,12,F30-minute programmes ` clearly
OL,13,Fsomething viewers would notice and
OL,14,Fsomething which could have an adverse
OL,15,Fimpact on the programme itself.
OL,17,FThe consultation runs until the end
OL,18,Fof May.
OL,3,CWhat would a change of PSB ad rules
OL,4,Cmean in practice?
